    "The Green Morocco Plan (2008-2020) aims to modernize agriculture and make it more resilient to climate change.",
    "It is advisable to align your wheat cultivation plans with these policies to benefit from potential government support.",
    "Given the future climate predictions, it would be prudent to consider the following:",
